Lek Scanner Android Debug APK Client v3.9.0
===========================================
This is the official debug companion signature package for Android (v3.9.0).
Use this debug companion to establish a direct hook with Termux or deploy locally on your device.

Installation steps for Debug App:
1. Copy this file into your android emulator or device.
2. If installing on some devices, verify 'Allow installation from unknown sources' is toggled.
3. Boot the application matching configuration with the Lek Scanner web service endpoint.
